videos.headline: Miami (OH) QB tosses ball straight to defender for pick-6
videos.description: Miami (OH) QB Brett Gabbert tries to throw a check down pass, but he throws it straight to Western Michigan LB Drake Spears, who returns it 74 yards for a touchdown.
